Output demo.gif

Set FontSize 17
Set Width 1100
Set Height 560
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set Padding 12
Set TypingSpeed 35ms

Hide
Type "export PATH=$PATH PS1='$ ' && rm -rf .claude skillet.lock.json my-skill && clear"
Enter
Show

Type "# a package manager for AI agent skills"
Sleep 900ms
Enter
Type "skillet search pdf"
Sleep 300ms
Enter
Sleep 2.2s

Type "skillet add pdf"
Sleep 300ms
Enter
Sleep 9s

Type "ls .claude/skills/pdf"
Sleep 300ms
Enter
Sleep 2.2s

Type "# write your own and share it on the registry"
Sleep 800ms
Enter
Type "skillet new my-skill && skillet validate ./my-skill"
Sleep 300ms
Enter
Sleep 4s
